1. 2. Top twenty rated movies (Condition: The movie should be rated/viewed by at least 40 users)

1) MyDriver.class : Execution of job will start from the Driver class here we specify 
all the mapper Reducer class.

here we have two table 
1. movies.dat : Movie information is in the file "movies.dat" and is in the following
format:
MovieID::Title::Genres

2. ratings.dat : All ratings are contained in the file "ratings.dat" and are in the
following format:

UserID::MovieID::Rating::Timestamp

2) MovieMapper.class: First we will get movie_id as a key and title as a value from movies.dat.

3) Rating Mapper.class: Then we will get movie_id as a key and rating as a value from the ratings.dat.

4) MyReducer.class: Here we join these two mapper and finally get movie_name as a key and average rating as a value.

5) SortingMapper.class :This is our 2nd job. it will take the output of the first job. here we pass average rating 
	as a key and movie_name as a value. because  we need to sort the output on the basis of  average rating.
	
6) SortingReducer.class : Here we place the condition for top 20 value and finally we will get the top 20 most
 rated movie and movie_name.